https://slackbuilds.org/repository/15.0/system/hfsprogs/?search=hfsprogs
hfs+ user space utils

The HFS+ file system used by Apple Computer for their Mac OS is 
supported by the Linux kernel.  Apple provides mkfs and fsck for HFS+ 
with the Unix core of their operating system, Darwin. This package is a 
port of Apple's tools for HFS+ filesystems